        "\n",
        "We validate this mechanism through an ablation study on the BRCA multi-omics dataset via step-wise modality inclusion. We simulate a high-dimensional rogue sensor (500 features, 20x variance) appended to biological views (RNA-Seq, CNV, Proteomics). As @tbl-brca-stepwise indicates, the model correctly ranks biological views, achieving a peak predictive AUC of **0.939** using only RNA-Seq, CNV, and Proteomics. Adding the Rogue modality correctly triggers weight suppression via the automated gating logic, preserving diagnostic representation integrity.\n",
